2.0.2.name: wordpress/plugin-jetradar-cheap-flights
2.0.2.description: Find and book cheap flights with this useful flight search plugin from Jetradar.com. Search and compare prices through dozens of travel websites with fewer clicks. Earn money with each purchase of airline tickets made by visitors of your website.
